Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:34.62,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,My name is\NIzumida Jun’ichirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:36.98,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,I am Yakushiji Ryouko’s confidant…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:38.49,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,… or so it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:42.33,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Today, I’m here with\Nmy boss at Narita Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.70,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,That’s because—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.06,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}Marianne, Lucienne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.27,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.26,Ryōko main,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}Yes, it’s been a while.{I think they say "une éternité".}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.49,Ryōko main,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}It’s great to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.91,Ryōko main,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}We missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:25.87,Ryōko title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fscx63\pos(194.3,88)\c&H0A1B6D&}Sixth File
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:31.96,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Marianne and Lucienne are two maids\Nwho work for Yakushiji Ryouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:36.67,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Of course, being maids, they do household chores, but that’s not everything they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.51,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Marianne is an expert\Nwith weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.71,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,and Lucienne is an expert\Nwith computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:44.31,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,She’s a genius when\Nit comes to hacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:47.64,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Say, Izumida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:51.35,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Why don’t you stop dozing\Nand join the conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.56,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I’m not\Ngood at speaking French.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.02,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,This country sure\Ndoesn’t change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.50,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Corrupt politicians and\Nbureaucratic scandals…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.28,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I’m surprised that\Nthis continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.16,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Of course it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:08.33,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,People just complain instead of doing something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:12.31,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,People just stay in their\Nterritory and complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.20,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,You’re right about that, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.50,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.48,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I believe you do {\i1}too much{\i0},\NSuperintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:27.27,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.14,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:39.53,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.52,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,If I knew this was going to happen, I would have brought my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.40,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Oh my, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.33,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.39,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.73,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I’ve notified the ones in charge at the Ginza Police Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.01,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:18.15,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,More importantly, what if the room next to us is red and has futons ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:23.61,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,How appropriate of you to play the role of the evil deputy official.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.18,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:28.78,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,I’m the sweet city girl\Nwho was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.33,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,What do you think about\Nthe incident earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.32,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I have no idea whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:41.64,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,One thing though. The victim may have had connections with the mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:42.70,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.59,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,The gun he held\Nwas a Tokarev.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.55,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:50.38,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Even if it was a Tokarev, was it as crudely modified as the guns used by the mafia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.64,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Let’s let the Ginza police\Nhandle this for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.14,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,That’s great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:59.48,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,I’m sure your Cabinet minister will be very happy once we settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:03.52,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Yes, he was pumped up about being able to use as much money as he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:04.84,Ryōko overlap,Ryo,0,0,0,,Two elite bureaucrats up to no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.34,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Do you know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:09.78,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Among bureaucrats,\Nthey’re somewhat famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.58,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,This one’s Aoyama from the Ministry of Defense. He’s known as Mr. Dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.63,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,That one is Isogai from the Ministry of Land, Infrastructure, Transport and Tourism.{This is long...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.57,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,He’s like the runner-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:21.00,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,So they have a cozy\Nrelationship with their dealers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.08,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,who then take\Nthem out to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.26,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,It’s the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:28.36,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,The saint’s maids\Nare quoting Latin.{What?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:33.63,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,After attending many dinners, they now\Nmanage dinners for various other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.98,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.93,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Where are those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:43.11,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,They went home ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.80,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,They probably wanted\Nto leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.63,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Good night, Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.00,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,We’ll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:03.67,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.30,Ryōko main,Gal,0,0,0,,Izumida-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.30,Ryōko overlap,Old,0,0,0,,Izumida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.34,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.18,Ryōko main,Gal,0,0,0,,We’ve experienced it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:12.08,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh Lord, protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.70,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,It was a ghost’s doing!\NI’m sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.55,Ryōko main,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:22.23,Ryōko main,Gal,0,0,0,,Last night, we were sorting material in the reference room downstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:24.34,Ryōko main,Gal,0,0,0,,just like the\Nsuperintendent instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.24,Ryōko main,Gal,0,0,0,,Oh my, is it an earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.44,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,That wasn’t an earthquake\Njust now, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.73,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,Do you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.71,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,So that’s what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.76,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,It wasn’t just the\NMetropolitan Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.63,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Jackie phoned me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.41,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,It seems a similar incident\Noccurred at the Ministry of Finance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.64,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Wakabayashi-san\Nexperienced it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.71,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,I think it’s just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.73,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,I should be better tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.65,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Yes, I’m terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.56,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.70,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,I’m scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.38,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,They’re waiting over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.46,Ryōko main,Mar,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.18,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Let’s go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.14,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,We stand out too much here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.50,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Just who are you calling\Na poikilothermic animal?{hurr durr big words}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.39,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Just who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:48.48,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,But Oyuki, you said you get\Ncold hands and feet easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:52.12,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,I wonder if your hands and feet\Nare cold because you’re cold inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:54.18,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,If I’m a cold-blooded animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:57.24,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,you’re a merciless\Ncold-blooded animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:01.36,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Oh my, there’s no one as warm as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:02.11,Ryōko overlap,Nis,0,0,0,,I’m surprised they don’t run out of topics to argue about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:05.36,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I’m sure it’s like your hobby.\NThey won’t get tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:08.38,Ryōko main,Nis,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, regarding my hobby, the leotard—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.84,Ryōko overlap,Jun,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nlet’s continue our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:11.67,Ryōko main,Nis,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:15.01,Ryōko main,Nis,0,0,0,,I may not look like it, but I’m a career bureaucrat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.97,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Well sorry for being\Na non-career bureaucrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.02,Ryōko main,Nis,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.75,Ryōko main,Nis,0,0,0,,Among us career bureaucrats,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:25.60,Ryōko main,Nis,0,0,0,,there have been rumors recently of ghost sightings and poltergeist phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.53,Ryōko main,Nis,0,0,0,,It looks like similar incidents have occurred at each ministry and government office.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.49,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:32.21,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,So that’s how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.84,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Oryou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.63,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,The Metropolitan Police,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.79,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,the Ministry of Land, Infrastructure, Transport and Tourism,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.54,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,the Ministry of Foreign Affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:39.97,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,the Ministry of Finance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:40.73,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,the Ministry of Agriculture,\NForestry and Fisheries,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.52,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,and the Ministry of Economy,\NTrade and Industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:44.54,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.79,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,The subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:51.13,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,The poltergeist causing the Kasumigaseki trouble is traveling via the subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.29,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,The Hibiya Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:55.72,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:09:02.85,Ryōko main,Ryo,60,60,0,,There’s a line that connects Yurakucho Line’s Sakuradamon Station with Chiyoda Line’s Kasumigaseki Station. Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.81,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,If it uses this line\Nto travel every night…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.60,Ryōko main,Jun,90,90,0,,Yes, it does line up with the ministries and government offices where the ghost incidents occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:15.34,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,But you said “it”.\NDo you mean…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:19.38,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,That’s right, the mysterious shadow we saw the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.04,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,It is probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.00,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,… the Underground Monster, Teradtron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.50,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Again with “Mystery, Thursday the Twelfth”?{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:43.95,Ryōko main,Gal,0,0,0,,This way, please, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:03.02,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.12,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Leave that there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:15.30,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Your men will regret it\Nif they see their boss like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:18.63,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,I don’t understand\Nthis fetish either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:19.53,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.82,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.16,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Things will get out of hand\Nif we don’t finish it off quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:51.46,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Even if we lied, blaming it on ghosts\Nor poltergeists, there {\i1}is{\i0} still a limit to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.09,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,That’s why you want to\Nmobilize my soldiers again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.85,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,So that’s how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:11.12,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,I’ve talked with Tokyo Metro,\Nvia their head office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:15.76,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,You didn’t have to\Nget their permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:17.11,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Please tell me,\NSuperintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.92,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What’s here\Nunder Kasumigaseki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.56,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Just wait until you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.58,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,Izumida-san,\Nplease be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:31.87,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I’m not worried since\NI’m with WTED Oryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:35.12,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,But she’s also SLD Oryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.17,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.13,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:09.87,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,That’s the line that connects Kasumigaseki and Sakuradamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:14.09,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,We’re just about underneath the Ministry of Foreign Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:21.59,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.14,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Don’t attack it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.44,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.69,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Because it’s Japan’s\Nnatural treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.40,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Is it the giant salamander?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.32,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Still, it’s huge…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.30,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Is this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:49.12,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes. This is the identity of Teradtron, the Underground Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.67,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,It doesn’t look\Nlike it’ll attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:58.63,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:13.65,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Normally, it eats small fish\Nand frogs, but it probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.40,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:22.18,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,It must have made\Nthis hole the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.06,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.83,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,The Hibiya\NCommon Utility Duct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.96,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,It’s an underground facility to connect various utility lines together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.72,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,So this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:43.88,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.63,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,We’re with the\NMetropolitan Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.13,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.97,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:52.99,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,You guys are the soldiers hired by the Ministry of Finance, the Ministry of Defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.35,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,and the Ministry of Land, Infrastructure, Transport and Tourism, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.31,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Bitch! How the hell\Ndo you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.36,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Heh, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.30,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,It’s the salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.59,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:29.23,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Damn it. It’s here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.68,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,That’s the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.06,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Call for reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:44.61,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,It probably thinks we’re food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.99,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,No, it might have just followed you here for no reason, Superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:48.81,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Why’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:55.27,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Well, I just thought it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:58.91,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What the hell is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.93,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,The underground facility that was built by the Imperial Japanese Army
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.29,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,in preparation for battles\Non the main island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.36,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,It was discovered during the construction of the Hibiya Common Utility Duct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.05,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,But the streets are…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:12.29,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,They decided to build a giant resort that only bureaucrats could visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.64,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,The public’s eyes can’t\Nreach the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:19.48,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Of course, it was built using money embezzled by every ministry and government office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.03,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,That’s tax money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.60,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,That’s what it’s called\Nby the side who pays.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.07,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,The side that uses it\Ndoesn’t think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.26,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.91,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,There’s no doubt\Nabout it. It’s after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.63,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.00,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.75,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Come with us, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:31.09,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\Nyou’re Izumida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.77,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:35.80,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,You’re WTED Oryou’s\Nsubordinate, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.15,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Actually, I have\Nsomething to ask you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.60,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,No, the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.11,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:02.33,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Our plan has suffered a setback due to the appearance of that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.73,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,The two of you are well known, even within the Ministry of Defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:11.09,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,I hear the two of you\Nare fairly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.68,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,If you have confidence\Nin your strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:17.59,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,I would like to ask you to\Nexterminate that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.02,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:22.31,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Of course, I will guarantee\Na return worthy of its price.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:25.76,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,I don’t want to say this, but you’re a non-career bureaucrat.{meeeh}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:29.63,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,The difference between you and the career bureaucrats will only grow bigger as you age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:31.95,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:37.03,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,If you’re going to live as a non-career bureaucrat, why not lend us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.40,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,You won’t be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:40.62,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,I will also promise you\Nsuccess in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:44.12,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,I don’t think\Nit’s a bad deal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.17,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.79,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,But, listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:53.44,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I am satisfied with being Yakushiji Ryouko’s subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.05,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.77,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Taking the upper hand just because we were being modest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.32,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.39,Ryōko main,Luc,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:26.33,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.83,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.39,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Damn you! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.27,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Above!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.74,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.20,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.87,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I’ve asked Abe Jun-san\Nfor reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.98,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,He said he’ll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:28.55,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,They should just be locked up for life underground with the natural treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.86,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}Okay. Start it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.23,Ryōko main,Two,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.55,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,An underground water vein?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:52.21,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Lucienne found it using data from the Ministry of Land, Infrastructure, Transport and Tourism.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:20:01.41,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Maybe it knew you’d do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:02.68,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.97,Ryōko main,Gal,0,0,0,,Assistant Inspector Izumida,\Nwhat are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.70,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,Ibuse Masuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:31.70,Ryōko tl notes,Note,0,0,0,,Note: “Sanshouuo” is Japanese for “salamander”.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:29.59,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,“Sanshouuo”.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.70,Ryōko main,Gal,0,0,0,,What is it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:36.48,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,I believe it was about a salamander which became too big to get out of its den.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:40.58,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,It complained\Nand gave excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:43.18,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,I read it when\NI was a student too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.12,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Yes, that’s what it was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:50.65,Ryōko italic,Ryo,0,0,0,,People just stay in their\Nterritory and complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.94,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,I heard from the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.28,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,You declined\Ntheir offer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.22,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:07.61,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,You said you were satisfied with your current position, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:08.91,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Th-That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:10.87,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,You did say it, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.33,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:18.67,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Why did you say\Nsomething so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:19.77,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:22.79,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,If you brought the natural\Ntreasure under your control
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:28.69,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,and beat up Mr. Dinner, I could have been ruling his underground world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.86,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Man, what a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.66,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Saying those things again…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.98,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Besides, their money is…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.27,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,No excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:40.61,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,As punishment, treat me to dinner at the restaurant we went to the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.75,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Of course, treat them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.74,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}Man, I’m starved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.82,Ryōko main,Two,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}Yes, so are we!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:54.37,Ryōko main,Two,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}Since Izumida-kun’s paying for this tonight, let’s order the chef’s special.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:18.18,Ryōko main,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}The people and events in this work are purely fictional.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:24.14,Ryōko main,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\blur5}Any resemblance to existing people or events is entirely coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.41,Ryōko main,Mar,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:27.27,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Inspector Maruoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.29,Ryōko main,Mar,0,0,0,,How about we go for a drink? Let’s keep it a secret from the Superintendent, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:31.38,Ryōko main,Mar,0,0,0,,It’s great to drink while complaining about your boss…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:35.51,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yakushiji Ryouko’s Supernatural Case File,\NFile Number 07: Okinawa, God’s Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.46,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:38.20,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,And? What were\Nyou going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.30,Ryōko main,Mar,0,0,0,,Wh-What—
